g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG3bq9zy.png&h=0f5575b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W6ZPRNU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW6ZPRNU.png&h=d5fcf362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zv9wkGf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZv9wkGf.png&h=1ce77d09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LTDANmg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLTDANmg.png&h=598e351f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44aa1594f1e0fc5b036085968f7ff2fe1a79ff1f","tid":1516597,"uid":231818,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBOnuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBOnuf.jpg&h=a519857e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報總編輯胡錫進尼左香港<br />\n佢話會去示威現場<br />\n同青年對話<br />\n佢對話完<br />\n係大陸人眼中實更有權威<br />\n到時輸出革命會更難<br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢落場時<br />\n準備定中共啲衰野<br />\n同一定要影住佢<br />\n錄低佢up過啲咩"},{"pid":"d6cb85be10b71cc5b0dfcd968e927bc752ff0c56","tid":1516597,"uid":228437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QVASPDm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQVASPDm.jpg&h=7dcb570c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5DzgwRH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5DzgwRH.jpg&h=0224a15b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vX31HYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvX31HYn.jpg&h=0834daef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F9Gyy43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF9Gyy43.jpg&h=df7eb643&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LuQ7DwJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai